{"tid":85791,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"日本婆婆 視 M$ EXCEL 為藝術","createTime":"2017-01-18T14:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T11:49:22.000Z","uid":1886,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4af6dc327b147eba804e492f41c913e72016f77b","tid":85791,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/title-11-770x439_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Ftitle-11-770x439_c.jpg&h=2ee026f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/01/17/%E6%97%A5%E8%80%86%E8%8B%B1%E5%8C%96excel%E7%82%BA%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2580%2586%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%258C%2596excel%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%2F&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8c134280\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/01/17/%E6%97%A5%E8%80%86%E8%8B%B1%E5%8C%96excel%E7%82%BA%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本一名退休耆英，因要照顧年長的母親而提早退休，但因此接觸到電腦平台。在學習電腦期間透過 Excel 去創作藝術，成為了她的第二事業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/l_tomomi_170112excel01-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fl_tomomi_170112excel01-1.jpg&h=1c049305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若宮正子自高中畢業後一直在銀行工作，在她 60 歲時為了照顧家中 90 歲的母親而提早退休。因此減少了出門的次數，令她的生活變得更加悶悶不樂。直到某天她從雑誌中看見一篇文章中說「只要擁有電腦，就算足不出戶都可以接觸他人」，就決定立刻去買電腦，開拓了她的創作生涯 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/l_tomomi_170112excel03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fl_tomomi_170112excel03.jpg&h=95dee473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若宮正子部分用 Excel 創作的圖案<br />\n<br />\n初初接觸電腦時，她認為只操作複雜困難，就算有教材教學要學習使用絕非一朝一夕之事。當打開 Excel 時更認為它是一排排煩人的數字排在一起，於是就抱著「要將 Excel 變成有趣創作軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」的心態去嘗試。最終經過一些創意和思考，她以線條和格子塗滿的方式作畫，將這個沈悶的試算表軟件變成了屬於她的畫布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/l_tomomi_170112excel09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fl_tomomi_170112excel09.jpg&h=041ef8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她更將自己創作的圖案印在不同的東西上。<br />\n<br />\n目前 83 歲的她不但創作了無數的藝術品，更將它們印刷在扇子、鎖匙扣上變成商品。還在近 10 年來在自己家裡開班教學，也到各大學演講，門生不計其數。此外她最近開始學習使用 3D Builder，將自己以往的作品 3D 化，可見薑還是老的比較辣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/l_tomomi_170112excel04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fl_tomomi_170112excel04.jpg&h=9f1bed6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她透過3D Build將一些舊作立體化。<br />\n<br />\n若宮正子於2014年 TEDxTokyo 中發表的演講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aP3IZbefkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3aP3IZbefkw&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=0499a73f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aP3IZbefkw</a>"},{"pid":"a5090142ed647f17aff8c55a15f3d90723366e70","tid":85791,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"a77c1f8bc85c1a49f844ce642d4faa9a49abb9a4","tid":85791,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/5dEVLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2F5dEVLB.png&h=2bd7413a&s={SIZE}\" /><br 